text: Raimond Lis (30 August 1888 - 21 December 1916) was a French gymnast. He competed in the men's team event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1888 births Category:1916 deaths Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:People from Armentières
